    public class SubstanceDispenseProposal
extends SubstanceClinicalStatementBase
    A clinical proposal for provision of a supply of a medication generally with the intention that it is subsequently consumed by a patient (usually in response to a prescription). An proposal for a substance to be dispensed but not administered. (E.g.,, �naloxone at bedside�).
